[SN]TITLE[SN]
Bath River Avon path safety railings installation begins

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Work has begun to install new safety railings on a path alongside a stretch of the River Avon in Bath where four men have drowned in the past year.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The Avon coroner ordered a safety audit after the deaths on the river by the downward slope from Green Park Road.
